    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "The type in question is `bytes3[2]`, a fixed-sized array of base type `bytes3`.\r\nSince it's fixed-sized, it does not match `T[]` (dynamically sized).\r\nIt also does not match `T[k] for any dynamic T` because `bytes3` is not dynamic (https://solidity.readthedocs.io/en/v0.5.9/types.html#fixed-size-byte-arrays).",
